title: CARISSA MOORE WINS 2013 MARGARET RIVER PRO
description: During a final filled with the biggest sets seen all day at Margaret River, Carissa Moore managed to escape a beating and grab a World Tour win instead! See more from Carissa at http://hurley.com/carissamoore
